pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `cliente` ( `Id_clie` int(8) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Est_clie` int(2) NOT NULL, `Nam_clie` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `Apel_clie` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `email_clie` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `Pass_clie` varchar(100) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_clie`), KEY `fk_clieest` (`Est_clie`), CONSTRAINT `fk_clieest` FOREIGN KEY (`Est_clie`) REFERENCES `est_usu` (`Id_est_usu`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=999948 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `detal_fact` ( `Id_comp` int(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Num_fact` int(20) NOT NULL, `id_prod` int(20) NOT NULL, `Cant_prod` int(3) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_comp`,`Num_fact`) USING BTREE, KEY `fk_prodeta` (`id_prod`), KEY `fk_facehmpl` (`Num_fact`), CONSTRAINT `fk_facehmpl` FOREIGN KEY (`Num_fact`) REFERENCES `factura` (`Num_fact`), CONSTRAINT `fk_prodeta` FOREIGN KEY (`id_prod`) REFERENCES `inventario` (`Id_prod`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1001 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `empleados` ( `ID_empl` int(3) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Est_usu` int(2) NOT NULL, `Sol_empl` int(8) NOT NULL, `Email_empl` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `Pass_emp` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `Obser_empl` varchar(225) NOT NULL, `Edad_empl` int(3) NOT NULL, `img_eml` longblob DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ID_empl`), KEY `fk_eplest` (`Est_usu`), KEY `fk_eplesol` (`Sol_empl`), CONSTRAINT `fk_eplesol` FOREIGN KEY (`Sol_empl`) REFERENCES `solic_emp` (`Id_sol_emp`), CONSTRAINT `fk_eplest` FOREIGN KEY (`Est_usu`) REFERENCES `est_usu` (`Id_est_usu`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2147483648 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `factura` ( `Num_fact` int(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Est_fact` int(2) NOT NULL, `Tip_pag` int(2) NOT NULL, `Id_cliente` int(8) DEFAULT NULL, `eple_fact` int(3) NOT NULL, `Fecha_fact` datetime NOT NULL, `Caja_fact` int(3) NOT NULL, `det_fac` int(20) NOT NULL, `Neto_val` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL, `Iva` int(3) NOT NULL, `Subtotal_Fac` int(20) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Num_fact`), KEY `fk_facempl` (`eple_fact`), KEY `fk_estfac_2` (`Id_cliente`), KEY `Est_fact` (`Est_fact`), KEY `fk_pago` (`Tip_pag`), CONSTRAINT `factura_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`Est_fact`) REFERENCES `est_fact` (`Id_est_fact`), CONSTRAINT `fk_estfac_2` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_cliente`) REFERENCES `cliente` (`Id_clie`), CONSTRAINT `fk_facempl` FOREIGN KEY (`eple_fact`) REFERENCES `empleados` (`ID_empl`), CONSTRAINT `fk_pago` FOREIGN KEY (`Tip_pag`) REFERENCES `tip_pag` (`Id_tip_pag`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1002 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `inventario` ( `Entra_2` int(20) NOT NULL, `Id_prod` int(20) DEFAULT NULL, `Entr_inv` int(3) DEFAULT NULL, `Sal_inv` int(3) DEFAULT NULL, `Saldo_inv` int(3) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Entra_2`), KEY `fk_inve_prod` (`Id_prod`), CONSTRAINT `fk_inve_prod` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_prod`) REFERENCES `producto` (`Id_prod`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `inve_has_detfac` ( `Entra_2` int(20) NOT NULL, `Id_comp` int(20) NOT NULL, KEY `fk_invedetfac_a` (`Entra_2`), KEY `fk_invedetfac_b` (`Id_comp`), CONSTRAINT `fk_invedetfac_a` FOREIGN KEY (`Entra_2`) REFERENCES `inventario` (`Entra_2`), CONSTRAINT `fk_invedetfac_b` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_comp`) REFERENCES `detal_fact` (`Id_comp`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `movi_inv` ( `Id_movi_inv` int(13) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Tip_mov_inv` int(2) NOT NULL, `Est_mov_inv` int(2) NOT NULL, `Entra_2_inv` int(20) NOT NULL, `Fecha_mov_inv` datetime NOT NULL, `Desc_mov_inv` varchar(250) NOT NULL, `Cant_mov_inv` int(3) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_movi_inv`), KEY `fk_movtip` (`Tip_mov_inv`), KEY `fk_movest` (`Est_mov_inv`), KEY `fk_moventr` (`Entra_2_inv`), CONSTRAINT `fk_moventr` FOREIGN KEY (`Entra_2_inv`) REFERENCES `inventario` (`Entra_2`), CONSTRAINT `fk_movest` FOREIGN KEY (`Est_mov_inv`) REFERENCES `estad_mov` (`Id_estad_mov`), CONSTRAINT `fk_movtip` FOREIGN KEY (`Tip_mov_inv`) REFERENCES `tip_mov` (`Id_tip_mov`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2002 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `producto` ( `Id_prod` int(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Est_prod` int(2) NOT NULL, `Tip_prod` int(2) NOT NULL, `Prov` int(8) NOT NULL, `Nam_prod` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `Carac_prod` varchar(250) NOT NULL, `Puntua_prod` float NOT NULL, `Val_prod` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL, `Iva_prod` int(3) NOT NULL, `Presen_prod` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `Tam_prod` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `img_prod` longblob NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_prod`), KEY `fk_Produc_EstProduc` (`Est_prod`), KEY `fk_Produc_Prov` (`Prov`), KEY `fk_Produc_Tiproduc` (`Tip_prod`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Produc_EstProduc` FOREIGN KEY (`Est_prod`) REFERENCES `estad_prod` (`Id_estad_prod`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Produc_Prov` FOREIGN KEY (`Prov`) REFERENCES `proveedor` (`Id_prov`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Produc_Tiproduc` FOREIGN KEY (`Tip_prod`) REFERENCES `tip_prod` (`Id_tip_prod`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=10000 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `proveedor` ( `Id_prov` int(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Empre_prov` int(2) NOT NULL, `Est_prov` int(2) NOT NULL, `Nam_prov` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `Cel_prov` int(10) DEFAULT NULL, `Tel_prov` int(10) DEFAULT NULL, `Cedu_prov` int(13) NOT NULL, `Dir_prov` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `Notas_prov` varchar(250) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_prov`), KEY `fk_provempre` (`Empre_prov`), KEY `fk_prove_est` (`Est_prov`), CONSTRAINT `fk_prove_est` FOREIGN KEY (`Est_prov`) REFERENCES `est_prov` (`Id_est_prov`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_provempre` FOREIGN KEY (`Empre_prov`) REFERENCES `empre_prov` (`Id_empre_prov`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1006 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `solic_emp` ( `Id_sol_emp` int(8) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Est_sol_emp` int(2) DEFAULT NULL, `Tip_usu` int(2) DEFAULT NULL, `Tip_doc_usu` int(2) DEFAULT NULL, `doc_usu` int(20) DEFAULT NULL, `Sol_emp` text DEFAULT NULL, `Email_sol` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL, `Nombre` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Pass_sol` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL, `Fecha_nac` datetime NOT NULL, `Fecha_sol` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_sol_emp`), KEY `fk_estsol` (`Est_sol_emp`), KEY `fk_Tip_usu` (`Tip_usu`), KEY `fk_tip_doc` (`Tip_doc_usu`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Tip_usu` FOREIGN KEY (`Tip_usu`) REFERENCES `tip_usu` (`Id_tip_usu`), CONSTRAINT `fk_estsol` FOREIGN KEY (`Est_sol_emp`) REFERENCES `est_sol` (`Id_est_sol`), CONSTRAINT `fk_tip_doc` FOREIGN KEY (`Tip_doc_usu`) REFERENCES `tip_doc` (`Id_tip_doc`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=86 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
